                            {
                                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger" href="logoff">Logoff</a></li>
                            }
                            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger" href="#portfolio">Products</a></li>
                            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger" href="#contact">Contact<a></li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </nav>
        
        <header class="masthead">
            <div class="container h-100">
                <div class="row h-100 align-items-center justify-content-center text-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-10 align-self-end">
                        <h1 class="text-uppercase text-white font-weight-bold text-center">Trucker Hats for Messy Buns</h1>
                        <hr class="divider my-4" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-8 align-self-baseline">
                        <p class="text-white-75 font-weight-light mb-5 text-center">
                            Plenty of beers and backyard BBQs later a friend said, "What about 'Truckette'?!?" and we had a winner. A big winner.  She also had to teach herself how to sew (again, from 8th grade home ec class) and then find the perfect lace, pick out colors, find hat suppliers, go to trade shows, listen to countless books on tape about business, learn how to cut vinyl and print and heat press art and then there was figuring out where to store it all! No lie, Truckette Hat Co has been run out of a storage unit for almost a year! Seriously...Stacie sits in a storage unit and cuts, sews, prints, boxes and ships Truckettes so that every chica in the world can snag a Truckette. The product you see today has been perfected through these past few years and we couldn't be more stoked.</p>
                        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-xl js-scroll-trigger" href="#about">Find Out More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <!-- About-->
        <section class="page-section bg-primary" id="about">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 text-center">
                        <h2 class="text-white mt-0">Hats that fit you and your lifestyle!</h2>
                        <hr class="divider light my-4" />
                        <p class="text-white-50 mb-4">We all want to let our inner self shine through. With so many costomizations to look through, you're sure to find the Truckette that fits you!</p>
                        <a class="btn btn-light btn-xl js-scroll-trigger" href="#services">Get Started!</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Services-->
        <section class="page-section" id="services">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="text-center mt-0">At Your Service</h2>
                <hr class="divider my-4" />
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
                        <div class="mt-5">
                            <i class="fas fa-4x fa-gem text-primary mb-4"></i>
                            <h3 class="h4 mb-2">Quality Materials</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-0">Truckettes are built to last. Made with quality materials and triple stitching in order to ensure that your truckette will stay with you through many adventures!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
                        <div class="mt-5">
                            <i class="fas fa-4x fa-laptop-code text-primary mb-4"></i>
                            <h3 class="h4 mb-2">Online Updates</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-0">We are commited to provide you with the most up to date Truckette news! Email notifications ensure that you won't miss out on our newest styles.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
                        <div class="mt-5">
                            <i class="fas fa-4x fa-globe text-primary mb-4"></i>
                            <h3 class="h4 mb-2">Direct Shipping</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-0">Truckettes orders are usually shipped next day!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
                        <div class="mt-5">
                            <i class="fas fa-4x fa-heart text-primary mb-4"></i>
                            <h3 class="h4 mb-2">Made with Love</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-0">Every hat is made with every ounce of love that we could possible fit!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Portfolio-->
        <section id="portfolio">
            <div class="container-fluid p-0">
                <div class="row no-gutters">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
                        <a class="portfolio-box" href="hats">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/HatsCat.jpg" alt=""/>
